#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an4.31"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.31:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.31:0.2"
msgid "4. Cakkavagga "
msgstr "4. Situations "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.31:0.3"
msgid "31. Cakkasutta "
msgstr "31. Situations "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.32, sc1
msgctxt "an4.31:1.1"
msgid "“Cattārimāni, bhikkhave, cakkāni, yehi samannāgatānaṃ devamanussānaṃ catucakkaṃ vattati, yehi samannāgatā devamanussā nacirasseva mahantattaṃ vepullattaṃ pāpuṇanti bhogesu. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these four situations. When these situations come about, any god or human who takes advantage of them will soon acquire great and abundant wealth. "

msgctxt "an4.31:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni cattāri? "
msgstr "What four? "

#. VAR: sappurisāvassayo → sappurisūpassayo (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "an4.31:1.3"
msgid "Patirūpadesavāso, sappurisāvassayo, attasammāpaṇidhi, pubbe ca katapuññatā—"
msgstr "Living in a suitable region, relying on good people, being rightly resolved in oneself, and past merit. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.31:1.4"
msgid "Imāni kho, bhikkhave, cattāri cakkāni, yehi samannāgatānaṃ devamanussānaṃ catucakkaṃ vattati, yehi samannāgatā devamanussā nacirasseva mahantattaṃ vepullattaṃ pāpuṇanti bhogesūti. "
msgstr "These are the four situations. When these situations come about, any god or human who takes advantage of them will soon acquire great and abundant wealth. "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an4.31:2.1"
msgid "Patirūpe vase dese, "
msgstr "When a person lives in a suitable region, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.31:2.2"
msgid "ariyamittakaro siyā; "
msgstr "making friends with noble ones, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.31:2.3"
msgid "Sammāpaṇidhisampanno, "
msgstr "possessing right resolve, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.31:2.4"
msgid "pubbe puññakato naro; "
msgstr "and having merit from the past, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.31:2.5"
msgid "Dhaññaṃ dhanaṃ yaso kitti, "
msgstr "grain, riches, fame, reputation, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.31:2.6"
msgid "sukhañcetaṃdhivattatī”ti. "
msgstr "and happiness come to them.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.31:2.7"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
